OL,3,CHospital trust investigated after the
OL,4,Cdeath of three patients
OL,6,FA criminal investigation is underway
OL,7,Finto a Leicestershire NHS Trust after
OL,8,Fthe death of three of its patients.
OL,10,FThe Leicestershire Partnership NHS
OL,11,FTrust (LPT) is being investigated for
OL,12,Foffences relating to corporate
OL,13,Fmanslaughter and gross negligence
OL,14,Fmanslaughter.
OL,16,FLeicestershire Police said today that
OL,17,Fits investigation follows three deaths
OL,18,Fbetween September 2020 and July 2021.
