OL,3,CHospital trust investigated after the
OL,4,Cdeath of three patients
OL,6,FWhile no charges have been brought
OL,7,Fagainst the trust, it's understood
OL,8,Fthat one of the deaths relates to the
OL,9,Fabsconding of a patient from the
OL,10,FBradgate Mental Health Unit at
OL,11,FGlenfield Hospital.
OL,13,FA recent employment tribunal heard
OL,14,Fthat the patient, named only as
OL,15,FPatient One in proceedings, was a new
OL,16,Farrival on the Beaumont Ward of the
OL,17,Funit in September 2020.
OL,19,FHe was able to escape from the ward's
OL,20,Fgarden before taking his own life, the
OL,21,Ftribunal was told.
