OL,3,CHospital trust investigated after the
OL,4,Cdeath of three patients
OL,6,FSafety concerns on the ward during
OL,7,FCovid were at the heart of the case,
OL,8,Fwith a former consultant claiming she
OL,9,Fwas forced out of her role after
OL,10,Fwhistleblowing over her fears around
OL,11,Fpatient safety.
OL,13,FPreviously, new arrivals at the
OL,14,Fhospital were split between wards.
