OL,3,CHospital trust investigated after the
OL,4,Cdeath of three patients
OL,6,FThe trust told that tribunal the
OL,7,Fadmissions ward was set up in response
OL,8,Fto NHS England's guidance in the early
OL,9,Fstages of the pandemic, adding it had
OL,10,Fhad "conversations" around controls to
OL,11,F"reduce" risks relating to the new
OL,12,Fstructure with "mitigations" being
OL,13,F"put in place".
OL,15,FWhile the police investigation
OL,16,Fcontinues, the trust says it would be
OL,17,F"inappropriate" for them to "comment.
